Package: itaka
Architecture: all
Depends: python (>=2.3), python-gtk2 (>= 2.10), python-twisted-web
Recommends: python-libnotify
Description: On-demand screenshooting server
 Itaka is a on-demand screenshooting server based on the HTTP protocol.
 It integrates a specifically coded server to take screenshots on-demand when
 your machine is queried through a remote browser. 
 .
 It features the following:
  * Supports PNG/JPEG (with quality adjustment) image types.
  * Supports client notifications through libnotify.
  * A very polished GTK+ GUI with detailed logging of activities.
